data.description: 3 bdrm 2 bath condo has a great view, a sense of privacy and all the great amenities; pool, spa, gym, business center, rec. room, clubhouse, and excellent schools. The pool and recreation area are stunning, the clubhouse elegant and useful. Great meeting rooms with your business in mind! This Condo is ready to move in. If you want a great lifestyle with no yard work and little maintenance. Close to skiing, shopping and restaurants. Don't miss this unique opportunity!   Some pictures are virtually staged. CIC Special Assessment Fee is Capital Contribution Fee based on 1/2 of 1% of listing price. Subject to change based on actual sale. Owner to include one year home warranty
